query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('colors',
'cookies',
'data.table',
'google-drive-api',
'integration',
'interop',
'ios5',
'mvvmcross',
'nuget',
'polymer',
'razor',
'response',
'typescript');
